《霍默的恐惧症》于1996年11月3日通过[[福克斯广播公司|福克斯广播公司]]在美国[[首演|首播]]<ref name="archive">{{cite web | title = Homer Phobia | accessdate = 2015-09-01 | work = The Simpsons Archive | archivedate = 2015-06-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150629112700/http://simpsonsarchive.com/episodes/4F11.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.simpsonsarchive.com/episodes/4F11.html}}</ref>。根据[[尼尔森收视率|尼尔森收视率]]调查结果，节目的收视率为8.7，在2月10至16日这周美国所有的电视节目中名列第47，并在这周福克斯的所有电视节目里排名第4<ref>{{cite news | title = NBC's sky falls on rest of TV's broadcast networks | date = 1997-02-21 | page = D-2 | publisher = The Florida Times-Union | author = David Bauder}}</ref>。节目赢得1997年[[黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]]不超1小时长度类杰出动画节目奖<ref >{{cite web | url = http://www.imdb.com/event/ev0000223/1997 | title = Awards for 1997 | work = IMDb | publisher = Amazon.com | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140825125545/http://www.imdb.com/event/ev0000223/1997 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-09-01 | archivedate = 2014-08-25}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.emmys.com/shows/simpsons | title = The Simpsons | accessdate = 2015-09-01 | publisher = Academy of Television Arts & Sciences | archivedate = 2015-06-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150708223237/http://www.emmys.com/shows/simpsons | deadurl = no}}</ref>。麦克·{{lang|en|B}}·安德森获[[安妮奖|安妮奖]]电视节目导演最佳个人成就奖<ref>{{cite web | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120208102825/http://annieawards.org/25thwinners.html | archivedate = 2012-02-08 | url = http://annieawards.org/25thwinners.html | title = Legacy: 25th Annual Annie Award Nominees and Winners (1997) | accessdate = 2012-02-08 | publisher = AnnieAwards.com}}</ref>，还在1998年世界动画庆典上获黄金时段电视剧最佳导演奖<ref name="origins" /><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.awn.com/mag/issue2.12/2.12pages/2.12wacintro.html | title = The World Animation Celebration: Pasadena's Festival | accessdate = 2015-09-01 | publisher = Animation World Magazine | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141203114248/http://www.awn.com/mag/issue2.12/2.12pages/2.12wacintro.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-12-03 | author = Kenyon, Heather}}</ref>。[[反诽谤男女同性恋联盟|反诽谤男女同性恋联盟]]称赞《霍默的恐惧症》是“将我们的社区以公平、风趣而又充满智慧的方式带上电视的光浑典范”<ref>{{cite news | title = Homer's Phobia? | date = 1997-02-21 | publisher = Gay & Lesbian Alliance Against Defamation}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://medialovesidentity.wordpress.com/2011/10/31/sexuality-and-gende/ | title = Sexuality and gender | date = 2011-10-31 | accessdate = 2015-09-02 | work = medialovesidentity | via = WordPress.com | archive-date = 2019-09-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190904045105/https://medialovesidentity.wordpress.com/2011/10/31/sexuality-and-gende/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>，并授予节目同志媒体奖杰出单集电视剧集奖<ref name="alberti">{{cite book | last = Henry | first = Matthew | editor = Alberti, John | year = 2003 | title = Leaving Springfield: The Simpsons and the Possibility of Oppositional Culture | chapter = Looking for Amanda Hugginkiss | publisher = Wayne State University Press | isbn = 0-8143-2849-0 | pages = 239–241}}</ref>。此外，本集的多个动画赛璐珞都于2001年获选在[[墨尔本|墨尔本]]的银{{lang|en|K}}画廊展示<ref name="origins" />。

=== 专业评价和分析 ===
有分析指出，《霍默的恐惧症》是《辛普森一家》探讨[[LGBT|女同性恋者、男同性恋者、双性恋者与跨性别者]]主题的重要组成部分<ref>{{cite news | title = Why America's love affair with The Simpsons is being forced out of the closet | date = 2004-08-07 | first = Andrew | last = Gumbel | work = Irish Independent}}</ref>。在此以前，《辛普森一家》也曾多次在剧集中涉及同性恋内容<ref name="Mudhar">{{cite news | author = Raju Mudhar | title = Springfield's coming-out party; Cartoon to reveal gay character And it might not be Smithers | publisher = ''Toronto Star'' | date = 2004-07-28 | page = A.03}}</ref>。例如1990年播出的第2季第2集《[[辛普森和达莉拉|辛普森和达莉拉]]》（{{lang|en|''Simpson and Delilah''}}）中就有卡尔（{{lang|en|Karl}}）亲吻霍默的镜头，常见角色[[韦伦·史密瑟斯|韦伦·史密瑟斯]]经常表现出对雇主[[蒙哥马利·伯恩斯|蒙哥马利·伯恩斯]]的爱意，这种爱意起初还比较含蓄，之后则变得露骨<ref>{{cite news | author = Stephen Kiehl | title = Homersexual debate splits Springfield | publisher = ''The Ottawa Citizen'' | date = 2005-02-12 | page = L.7}}</ref>。但是，《霍默的恐惧症》却是节目首次完全围绕同性恋主题展开。《辛普森一家》之后还会多次探讨{{lang|en|LGBT}}相关议题，如第14季的第17集《[[秃鹰3个同性恋|秃鹰3个同性恋]]》（{{lang|en|''Three Gays of the Condo''}}）和第16季第10集《[[我为结婚狂|我为结婚狂]]》（{{lang|en|''There's Something About Marrying}}）<ref name="Outing">{{cite news | title = Springfield awaits its first outing | publisher = ''Calgary Herald'' | date = 2004-07-29 | page = E.2}}</ref>。

节目播出后，剧组收到的正面反响占绝大多数，对内容不满的观众“极少”<ref name="com" />。艾伦·弗鲁特金（{{lang|en|Alan Frutkin}}）在{{lang|en|LGBT}}阵营杂志《[[倡导者|倡导者]]》（{{lang|en|''The Advocate''}}）给予本集正面评价，称其为“最佳《辛普森一家》”<ref>{{cite news | title = Homer's Sexual Panic | author = Frutkin, Alan | work = The Advocate | date = 1997-02-18 | page = 53 | issue = 727}}</ref>。沃伦·马丁（{{lang|en|Warren Martyn}}）和阿德里安·伍德（{{lang|en|Adrian Wood}}）在著作《我简直不敢相信这是更大更新的辛普森一家非官方指南》（{{lang|en|''I Can't Believe It's a Bigger and Better Updated Unofficial Simpsons Guide''}}）一书中表示：“只有《辛普森一家》才能把这个话题用如此准确传神而又幽默的方式表达出来，实在太棒了”<ref name="BBC" />。马修·亨利（{{lang|en|Matthew Henry}}）在《[[离开春田镇|离开春田镇]]》（{{lang|en|''Leaving Springfield''}}）一书中称赞节目敢于批判“对同性恋最常见的误解，以为同性恋是某种具有传染性的东西”，书中对剧集的其它主题也有正面评价<ref name="alberti" />。[[悉尼大学|悉尼大学]]的凯瑟琳·隆比（{{lang|en|Catharine Lumby}}）认为，节目得以成功地在没有过度[[政治正确|政治化]]的情况下仍然以相当深刻的方式探索了许多同性恋问题，从这个角度上来说，《霍默的恐惧症》堪称典范，她还进一步指出，这集将批判同性恋恐惧症的立场通过幽默形式表现出来，比诸如《[[同志亦凡人_(2000年电视剧)|同志亦凡人]]》之类其他同性恋主题电视节目更加成功<ref>{{cite news | title = Mmmmmmmm ... clever | work = The Age | author = Michael Lallo | date = 2007-07-25 | page = Culture 9}}</ref>。托德·吉尔克里斯特（{{lang|en|Todd Gilchrist}}）在评价《辛普森一家》第8季{{lang|en|DVD}}时称，《霍默的恐惧症》“无疑是有史以来最伟大的电视剧集之一”<ref>{{cite web | date = 2006-08-14 | work = IGN.com | author = Gilchrist, Todd | url= http://uk.ign.com/articles/2006/08/14/the-simpsons-the-complete-eighth-season | archivedate = 2013-10-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131014191040/http://uk.ign.com/articles/2006/08/14/the-simpsons-the-complete-eighth-season | deadurl = no | title = The Simpsons – The Complete Eighth Season | accessdate = 2015-09-02}}</ref>。

2003年初，《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》评选最优秀的25集《辛普森一家》，本集名列第5<ref>{{cite web|deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018160211/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C417748~3~0~25bestand1%2C00.html |archivedate=2014-10-18 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,417748~3~0~25bestand1,00.html |title=The Family Dynamic |accessdate=2014-10-18 |date=2003-01-29 |publisher=Entertainment Weekly }}</ref>。《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》于同年发文，列出[[辛普森一家档案馆|辛普森一家档案馆]]网站管理员评选的《辛普森一家》十佳剧集，本集正好排在第10位<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131012022320/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2003-02-06-fan-favorites_x.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2003-02-06-fan-favorites_x.htm | title = 10 fan favorites | accessdate = 2015-09-02 | author = Paakkinen, Jouni | date = 2003-02-06 | publisher = USA Today | archivedate = 2013-10-12 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，{{lang|en|AskMen.com}}网站也在评选节目十佳剧集时把《霍默的恐惧症》排在第10名<ref>{{cite web | url = http://uk.askmen.com/top_10/entertainment/64_top_10_list.html | title = Top 10: Simpsons Episodes | accessdate = 2015-09-02 | author = Weir, Rich | publisher = Askmen.com | archivedate = 2015-04-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150403140129/http://uk.askmen.com/top_10/entertainment/64_top_10_list.html | deadurl = no}}</ref>。2010年初，{{lang|en|[[IGN|IGN.com]]}}网站评选《辛普森一家》历史上最优秀的客串演出，约翰·沃特斯在本集中的表现名列第9<ref>{{cite web | url = http://uk.ign.com/articles/2010/01/04/top-25-simpsons-guest-appearances?page=4 | title = Top 25 Simpsons Guest Appearances | accessdate = 2015-09-02 | author1 = Goldman, Eric | author2 = Iverson, Dan | author3 = Zoromski, Brian | publisher = IGN | archivedate = 2013-10-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131014114543/http://uk.ign.com/articles/2010/01/04/top-25-simpsons-guest-appearances?page=4}}</ref>，并且在《[[电视指南_(美国杂志)|电视指南]]》2007年5月举行的类似评选上排名更高，达到第3位<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.tvguide.com/news/simpsons-turns-400-40534/ | title = The Simpsons Turns 400: We Name the Greatest Guests! | accessdate = 2015-09-02 | author = Arnold Wayne Jones | publisher = TV Guide | date = 2007-05-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150527122518/http://www.tvguide.com/news/simpsons-turns-400-40534/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-05-27}}</ref>。2012年，《娱乐周刊》评选《辛普森一家》历史上最出色的21位客串名星，沃特斯同样榜上有名（第19位）<ref>{{cite news | title = 'The Simpsons:' 21 Great Guest Stars | publisher = Entertainment Weekly | date = 2012-02-20 | author = Wook Kim | url = http://www.ew.com/gallery/simpsons-21-great-guest-stars/577859_john-waters | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150902030928/http://www.ew.com/gallery/simpsons-21-great-guest-stars/577859_john-waters | accessdate = 2015-09-02 | archivedate = 2015-09-02}}</ref>。约翰·帕特森（{{lang|en|John Patterson}}）在《[[卫报|卫报]]》上称，沃特斯在《霍默的恐惧症》中的形象“在我看来就像过去25年来最具影响的流行文化人物齐聚一堂”<ref>{{cite news | title = The Guide: Preview film: If only... There were a few taboos left for John Waters to shatter. John Patterson mourns the death of offensiveness | url = https://archive.org/details/divorceguideforw0000patt | author = John Patterson | work = The Guardian | date = 2005-04-30}}</ref>。

2002年，“关掉电视”（{{lang|en|Off The Telly}}）网站的史蒂夫·威廉姆斯（{{lang|en|Steve Williams}}）和伊恩·琼斯（{{lang|en|Ian Jones}}）在评论中批评《霍默的恐惧症》是《辛普森一家》历史上最糟糕的5集节目之一，称其品味低劣，“给人嘴里留下那么讨厌的味道”，整个剧情中的霍默“完全就是个混蛋”。两人还称，“这正是我们之前没有在节目中看到的一个方面，而且也不怎么想看到。”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.offthetelly.co.uk/?page_id=382 | title = Five Of The Best ... And Five Of The Worst | accessdate = 2012-05-13 | author = Williams, Steve; Jones, Ian | publisher = Off the Telly | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121114085528/http://www.offthetelly.co.uk/?page_id=382 | archivedate = 2012-11-14}}</ref>2003年6月，伊戈尔·斯麦科夫（{{lang|en|Igor Smykov}}）起诉俄罗斯{{lang|en|[[REN_TV|REN TV]]}}电视台，指责该台播放《辛普森一家》和《[[居家男人|居家男人]]》这类“道德败坏，会加剧毒品、暴力和同性恋”的电视节目，并请法官观看《霍默的恐惧症》，称这集节目证明《辛普森一家》宣扬同性恋，因此不能再在电视上播出。经过1天的审讯，法庭驳回了这起案件<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.sptimes.ru/story/3199 | title = Court Rules for Simpsons Cartoon | accessdate = 2014-12-26 | work = The St. Petersburg Times | date = 2005-04-05 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141226055017/http://www.sptimes.ru/story/3199 | archivedate = 2014-12-26}}</ref>。

